### 1. Baseball-only Trainer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "baseball-coach@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Coach Mike",
  "role": "TRAINER",
  "bio": "Baseball hitting specialist",
  "sports": ["BASEBALL"]
}

> {%
    client.global.set("trainer_token", response.body.token);
%}

###

### 2. Softball-only Trainer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "softball-coach@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Coach Sarah",
  "role": "TRAINER",
  "bio": "Softball pitching specialist",
  "sports": ["SOFTBALL"]
}

###

### 3. Both Sports Trainer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "both-coach@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Coach John",
  "role": "TRAINER",
  "bio": "Teaches both baseball and softball",
  "sports": ["BASEBALL", "SOFTBALL"]
}

###

### 4. Trainer Views Profile
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trainers/me
Authorization: Bearer {{trainer_token}}

###

### 5. Trainer Updates Sports (Changes to both)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/trainers/me
Authorization: Bearer {{trainer_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sports": ["BASEBALL", "SOFTBALL"]
}

###

### 6. Public Views All Trainers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trainers